      "why": "**Why reset on mismatch?** Subsequences may skip characters (so they carry forward\n`max(...)`); substrings cannot. Zeroing on mismatch encodes \"the contiguous run ended\nhere.\" Contrasting this with LCS makes the subsequence-vs-substring distinction concrete.",
